data.description: $179,000.  Gorgeous 2017 3bed-2ba home, open concept floorplan with attached 2 car garage very close to town and all the conveniences. This home offers shaker Kitchen cabinets, a nice pantry for lots of storage and stainless appliances.  Home also has plantation shutters and recessed lighting throughout! Master suite has a large walk-in closet, dual sinks and a tiled shower/jetted tub! Backyard has a 10x10 open deck! This home is well maintained and ready for your touch!
